<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">移位结合法，在有括号的算式中，如果几个数的积除以几个数的积，可以通过“移位结合”，使计算简便。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">(42×24)÷(14×8)=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> (42×24)÷(14×8)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(42÷14)×(24÷8)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3×3</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=9</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>